text: Linda Kronenberg (born 6 October 1990) is a Swiss female volleyball player. She played at the 2017 Montreux Volley Masters, 2018 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2019 Montreux Volley Masters. She played for Volley Koniz and VFM Franches-Montagnes. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Swiss volleyball players Category:Living people
